{"tid":1053871,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"過去一年磨過 2xx 把刀 你問我答 (2)","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T06:46:01.000Z","uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b84cc43be5c4b72f81e9e89e76a9d2cdea194dce","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"由於上一個post出現左D誤會同埋沉底<br />\n我就係到整理一下之前打既文章<br />\n上一個post 既 link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1048029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1048029/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">澄清翻:我唔係Alan 我唔係KTH Kitchen</span></span></strong><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n是咁的，喺廚藝學院讀緊嘅時候，學校啲刀 9 成都係鈍到阿媽都唔認得, 每日都要拎住把間尺同啲食材搏命，久而久之終於頂唔順，萌生要磨刀嘅諗法。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，我唔識。<br />\n<br />\n我開始會問下阿 sir 點磨，不過用完阿 sir 教既方法都無咩用。所以我就開始上網搵資料、睇片、爬文，再不停用學校屋企嘅刀實習。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我得到磨刀技能一個。自此我就開始每日幫屋企人、朋友、親戚、街坊磨刀&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAny肥，我喺幫人磨刀嘅過程發現, 普遍香港人對於「刀」嘅知識係接近零。<br />\n<br />\n例如真係有好多人唔知刀係有得磨，覺得係消耗品, 用鈍咗就會買把新。<br />\n有啲就用咗幾十年都無磨過把刀，日日都係會用把鐵尺壓開啲食物。<br />\n多數家庭主婦或者 home cook 認識刀具嘅牌子, 都停留喺係孖X牌同陳X記。<br />\n<br />\n所以我就想喺到, 拋磚引玉, 講下一 D 刀嘅知識, 等連登仔唔使再俾人搵笨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16649b7895015018a4f9ac967b31710eb01c912b","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:47:23.000Z","msg":"咁我就講下D簡單野先<br />\n<br />\n世上咁多唔同刀型<br />\n中式有「片刀」、「文武刀」...<br />\n西式有「主廚刀 (Chef&rsquo;s knife)」、「牛刀」...<br />\n日式有「出刃」、「柳刃」...<br />\n仲有好多好多...<br />\n<br />\n到底我要需要咩刀呢?<br />\n<br />\n其實一般屋企用嘅話, 我會推薦用<br />\n「三德刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJtW8RJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJtW8RJ.jpg&h=9baf773c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「主廚刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHViCK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHViCK8.jpg&h=476d2139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「文武刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqbqhLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqbqhLa.jpg&h=5bd1be50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為屋企處理食材相對簡單, 唔需要針對特別嘅食材, 要用特別嘅刀<br />\n所以家用刀會以萬用 or 多用途做首要條件<br />\n依三種刀功能上都差唔多, 切片、條、絲、丁、粒都無問題<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅分別在於唔同既切野手法<br />\n「文武刀」同「三德刀」傾向平推嘅切法<br />\n而主廚刀就傾向Rock Chop (Gordon Ramsay 嗰種切法)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z_d0soK1cI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5z_d0soK1cI&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=13a66dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z_d0soK1cI</a> (12分鐘個到)<br />\n所以只係睇你慣用咩手勢切野, 無話邊種好D<br />\n而家搵一種適合你, 或者你鍾意嘅手勢"},{"pid":"8ccc2baa899de298c8c8f3db2960ce0be159733e","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"上面講左刀型既分別，咁下面講深入少少<br />\n<br />\n我地成日聽「不鏽鋼」乜「不鏽鋼」乜<br />\n其實不鏽鋼只係一個鋼材種類，不鏽鋼入面有多唔同既鋼<br />\n例如 VG10 AUS8 1.14116....... N百種<br />\n但簡單D講白D，其實係硬度既分別。<br />\n<br />\n硬度單位係HRC (Rockwell hardness)<br />\n數字愈大愈硬，反之亦然。<br />\n同常用係廚刀上既硬度介乎53-67 左右<br />\n愈硬就鋒利度保持得愈耐，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係愈硬愈好，因為愈硬=愈脆<br />\n所以愈硬既刀泛用性愈低<br />\n軟身鋼就易鈍D，不過佢唔易崩，斬骨無問題<br />\n<br />\n所以講到尾都係睇自己需要，無絕對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6956f08930859907f9c0056b149d19522d57bbf","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"請問識唔識磨鉸剪？"},{"pid":"e840fd989f578b9a250be4f2c85955b15528982d","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6956f08930859907f9c0056b149d19522d57bbf","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"請問識唔識磨鉸剪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔係太識 只係磨過十把左右"},{"pid":"ac7bca9a3be3249c20c00268fd81da90cc7dedfd","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e840fd989f578b9a250be4f2c85955b15528982d","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6956f08930859907f9c0056b149d19522d57bbf","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"請問識唔識磨鉸剪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔係太識 只係磨過十把左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"廚剪？"},{"pid":"dfc5227ffb7f0f57d528b11ef80e6141d9856e35","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7bca9a3be3249c20c00268fd81da90cc7dedfd","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e840fd989f578b9a250be4f2c85955b15528982d","tid":1053871,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6956f08930859907f9c0056b149d19522d57bbf","tid":1053871,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"請問識唔識磨鉸剪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔係太識 只係磨過十把左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"廚剪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"剪布個D"}]}